---
// Download section component
---

<section id="download" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Jetzt herunterladen
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        LoopCut ist bald im App Store verfügbar. 
        Melde dich an, um benachrichtigt zu werden, sobald die App veröffentlicht wird.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Download Info -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Bald verfügbar im App Store
        </h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Kostenlos</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Keine versteckten Kosten oder Abonnements</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Datenschutz-konform</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Deine Daten bleiben bei dir - DSGVO-konform</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">KI-gestützt</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Intelligente Analyse und Planung</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- System Requirements -->
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Systemanforderungen</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Betriebssystem:</span>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 block">iOS 15.0 oder neuer</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Speicherplatz:</span>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 block">50 MB verfügbar</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Internet:</span>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 block">Für KI-Analyse erforderlich</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Sprache:</span>
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-900 block">Deutsch</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Email Signup -->
        <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-primary-200">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">
            Benachrichtigung bei Veröffentlichung
          </h4>
          <p class="text-primary-700 text-sm mb-4">
            Erhalte eine E-Mail, sobald LoopCut im App Store verfügbar ist.
          </p>
          <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
            <input
              type="email"
              placeholder="deine@email.de"
              class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent"
              required
            />
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              Benachrichtigen
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- App Store Mockup -->
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- App Store Badge Placeholder -->
          <div class="w-80 h-96 bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-2">App Store</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4">Badge wird hier angezeigt</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-300 text-gray-600 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm">
                Bald verfügbar
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Decorative Elements -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-200 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-6 h-6 bg-primary-300 rounded-full opacity-50"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Info -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Häufig gestellte Fragen
        </h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-left max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Ist LoopCut wirklich kostenlos?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Ja, LoopCut ist vollständig kostenlos. Es gibt keine versteckten Kosten oder Abonnements.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Werden meine Daten sicher gespeichert?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Deine Daten werden lokal auf deinem Gerät gespeichert und sind DSGVO-konform geschützt.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Funktioniert die App offline?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Du kannst Gedanken offline sammeln. Die KI-Analyse benötigt eine Internetverbindung.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Gibt es eine Android-Version?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Aktuell entwickeln wir LoopCut für iOS. Eine Android-Version ist für die Zukunft geplant.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 